{"title":"鸟瞰（二首）","authors":["赵大昕"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":2,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸟瞰（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵大昕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵上有一颗露珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着干涸了的湖底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出一声轻轻的嘲讽："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这算是什么湖泊！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈焰炙烤着大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷起阵阵热风——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咦，露珠怎么不见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵也低垂美丽的额？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山间有两条小溪奔来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左冲右突，清流如注——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花朵重又露出了笑容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映着一池粼粼的碧波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵霹雷闪过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有片森林起了火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不远处，小树歪斜着头："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“烧吧！反正烧不着我！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火越燃越猛，扑腾着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灼伤小树娇嫩的皮肤……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火越烧越近，蔓延着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把小树整个儿吞没……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几条戴红臂章的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开出一道防火沟——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火灭了，又捧把焦土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"培在小树裸露的根部。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}